🏛️ I’m incredibly proud to be invited to share my story in Paris at one of the most prestigious Universities in the world, La Sorbonne. 🇫🇷

A special “Here we go” panel will take place in Paris on Wednesday, May 7th ahead of Champions League semi final between PSG and Arsenal this week.

Special thanks Université Paris 1 Panthéon-Sorbonne, Sorbonne School of Economics, Formation Continue Pantheón-Sorbonne… can’t wait to be there! 👋🏻😁
